<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>참고문헌 검증 리포트 — {{ report.metadata.draft_title }}</title>
<style>
  body {
    font-family: -apple-system, "Apple SD Gothic Neo", "Noto Sans KR", sans-serif;
    max-width: 920px;
    margin: 2em auto;
    padding: 0 1.2em;
    color: #1c1c1e;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 1.7em;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #222;
    padding-bottom: 0.3em;
    margin-bottom: 0.4em;
  }
  h2 { font-size: 1.2em; margin-top: 2em; }
  .meta-row {
    color: #666;
    font-size: 0.9em;
    margin-bottom: 1em;
  }
  .meta-row span { margin-right: 1.2em; }
  .banner {
    background: #fff7e6;
    border-left: 4px solid #ff9800;
    padding: 0.8em 1em;
    margin: 1em 0 1.5em;
    font-size: 0.92em;
  }

  /* ----- Summary metrics ----- */
  .summary {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 0.7em;
    margin: 1em 0 0.5em;
  }
  .summary-cell {
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 0.7em 0.9em;
    background: #fafafa;
  }
  .summary-cell .count { font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.2; }
  .summary-cell .label { color: #777; font-size: 0.82em; margin-top: 0.2em; }
  .status-line { margin: 0.7em 0 0; font-size: 0.95em; }
  .status-line .seg { margin-right: 1.1em; }

  /* ----- Reference card ----- */
  .ref-card {
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1em 1.2em;
    margin: 1.1em 0;
    background: #fff;
    page-break-inside: avoid;
  }
  .ref-card.status-hallucination  { border-left: 5px solid #c62828; }
  .ref-card.status-metadata_error { border-left: 5px solid #ef6c00; }
  .ref-card.status-unverifiable   { border-left: 5px solid #6a1b9a; }
  .ref-card.status-verified       { border-left: 5px solid #2e7d32; }

  .ref-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    margin-bottom: 0.4em;
  }
  .ref-header .idx { color: #999; font-size: 0.9em; margin-right: 0.5em; }
  .ref-header .ref-title { font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.05em; }
  .ref-header .status-badge {
    font-size: 0.85em;
    padding: 0.15em 0.55em;
    border-radius: 3px;
    color: #fff;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .badge-verified       { background: #2e7d32; }
  .badge-metadata_error { background: #ef6c00; }
  .badge-hallucination  { background: #c62828; }
  .badge-unverifiable   { background: #6a1b9a; }

  .ref-meta {
    color: #666;
    font-size: 0.9em;
    margin-bottom: 0.4em;
  }
  .ref-summary {
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0.4em 0 0.6em;
  }
  .ref-raw {
    color: #888;
    font-size: 0.85em;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 0.6em;
    word-break: break-word;
  }

  /* ----- Diff table ----- */
  .diff-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin: 0.6em 0;
    font-size: 0.92em;
  }
  .diff-table th {
    background: #f5f5f5;
    text-align: left;
    padding: 0.45em 0.6em;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
  }
  .diff-table td {
    padding: 0.5em 0.6em;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    vertical-align: top;
    word-break: break-word;
  }
  .diff-table .col-field { width: 100px; font-weight: 600; }
  .diff-table .col-user { color: #c62828; }
  .diff-table .col-canon { color: #2e7d32; }
  .diff-table .sev-critical { color: #c62828; }
  .diff-table .sev-major    { color: #ef6c00; }
  .diff-table .sev-minor    { color: #757575; }
  .diff-table .sev-info     { color: #1976d2; }

  /* ----- Content findings ----- */
  .content-finding {
    background: #fffbe6;
    border-left: 3px solid #f9a825;
    padding: 0.7em 0.9em;
    margin: 0.6em 0;
    border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
  }
  .content-finding .cf-header {
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5em;
  }
  .content-finding .cf-pair {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0.7em;
    margin: 0.4em 0;
  }
  .content-finding .cf-pair .cf-side h5 {
    margin: 0 0 0.25em;
    font-size: 0.85em;
    color: #555;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .content-finding .cf-pair .cf-quote {
    padding: 0.5em 0.7em;
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: #333;
    font-size: 0.9em;
    word-break: keep-all;
    overflow-wrap: break-word;
  }
  .content-finding .cf-pair .cf-quote.cf-draft {
    background: #fff3f3;
    border-left: 3px solid #c62828;
  }
  .content-finding .cf-pair .cf-quote.cf-source {
    background: #f1f8e9;
    border-left: 3px solid #2e7d32;
  }
  .content-finding .cf-pair .cf-quote em.empty {
    color: #999;
  }
  .content-finding .cf-explanation {
    margin: 0.4em 0;
    color: #444;
    font-size: 0.92em;
  }
  .content-finding .cf-suggestion {
    background: #e8f5e9;
    padding: 0.45em 0.7em;
    border-radius: 3px;
    margin-top: 0.4em;
    font-size: 0.92em;
  }
  .content-finding .cf-extra {
    margin-top: 0.5em;
    color: #888;
    font-size: 0.85em;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .content-finding .cf-pair { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  .hall-explainer {
    background: #ffebee;
    border-left: 3px solid #c62828;
    padding: 0.7em 0.9em;
    margin: 0.6em 0;
    border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
    font-size: 0.92em;
  }

  .orphan-section { margin-top: 2em; }
  .orphan-section .orphan-item {
    border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    border-left: 4px solid #0277bd;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 0.6em 0.9em;
    margin: 0.5em 0;
    font-size: 0.92em;
  }

  @media print {
    body { max-width: 100%; }
    .ref-card { box-shadow: none; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>참고문헌 검증 리포트</h1>
  <div class="meta-row">
    <span><b>문서:</b> {{ report.metadata.draft_title }}</span>
    <span><b>처리 시간:</b> {{ "%.1f"|format(report.metadata.processing_seconds) }}초</span>
    <span><b>비용:</b> ${{ "%.3f"|format(report.metadata.total_usd_cost) }}</span>
    <span><b>검증 레벨:</b> {{ report.metadata.verification_level }}</span>
  </div>

  <div class="banner">
    <b>⚠️ 보조 도구입니다.</b>
    모든 판정은 LLM·API 출력이며 오판 가능성이 있습니다. 최종 결정은 직접 확인해주세요.
  </div>

  {# ---------- Summary ---------- #}
  <h2>요약</h2>
  {% set status_count = namespace(verified=0, metadata_error=0, hallucination=0, unverifiable=0) %}
  {% for v in report.references %}
    {% if v.status == "verified" %}{% set status_count.verified = status_count.verified + 1 %}
    {% elif v.status == "metadata_error" %}{% set status_count.metadata_error = status_count.metadata_error + 1 %}
    {% elif v.status == "hallucination" %}{% set status_count.hallucination = status_count.hallucination + 1 %}
    {% elif v.status == "unverifiable" %}{% set status_count.unverifiable = status_count.unverifiable + 1 %}
    {% endif %}
  {% endfor %}
  {% set n_problem = status_count.metadata_error + status_count.hallucination + status_count.unverifiable %}
  <div class="summary">
    <div class="summary-cell">
      <div class="count">{{ report.references|length }}</div>
      <div class="label">총 참고문헌</div>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-cell">
      <div class="count" style="color:#c62828">{{ n_problem }}</div>
      <div class="label">문제 있음</div>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-cell">
      <div class="count">{{ "%.0f"|format(report.metadata.processing_seconds) }}초</div>
      <div class="label">처리 시간</div>
    </div>
    <div class="summary-cell">
      <div class="count">${{ "%.3f"|format(report.metadata.total_usd_cost) }}</div>
      <div class="label">총 비용</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="status-line">
    {% if status_count.verified %}<span class="seg" style="color:#2e7d32">✅ 검증됨 {{ status_count.verified }}</span>{% endif %}
    {% if status_count.metadata_error %}<span class="seg" style="color:#ef6c00">🟠 메타데이터 오류 {{ status_count.metadata_error }}</span>{% endif %}
    {% if status_count.hallucination %}<span class="seg" style="color:#c62828">🔴 환각 의심 {{ status_count.hallucination }}</span>{% endif %}
    {% if status_count.unverifiable %}<span class="seg" style="color:#6a1b9a">❓ 확인 불가 {{ status_count.unverifiable }}</span>{% endif %}
  </p>

  {# ---------- Reference cards ---------- #}
  <h2>참고문헌별 검증 결과</h2>

  {# Sort refs by status priority — hallucination first, verified last #}
  {% set ordered_refs = [] %}
  {% for status_name in ["hallucination", "metadata_error", "unverifiable", "verified"] %}
    {% for v in report.references if v.status == status_name %}
      {%- set _ = ordered_refs.append(v) -%}
    {% endfor %}
  {% endfor %}

  {% for vref in ordered_refs %}
    {% set ref = vref.canonical or vref.reference %}
    {%- set all_cf = report.findings|selectattr("category", "equalto", "content_mismatch")|selectattr("reference_id", "equalto", vref.reference.id)|list -%}
    {%- set cfs = all_cf[:2] -%}
    <div class="ref-card status-{{ vref.status }}">
      <div class="ref-header">
        <div>
          <span class="idx">#{{ loop.index }}</span>
          <span class="ref-title">
            {% if ref.authors %}{{ ref.authors[0].family }}{% if ref.authors|length > 1 %} et al.{% endif %}{% else %}(저자 없음){% endif %}
            {% if ref.year %} ({{ ref.year }}){% endif %}
            — {{ ref.title or "(제목 없음)" }}
          </span>
        </div>
        <span class="status-badge badge-{{ vref.status }}">
          {% if vref.status == "verified" %}✅ 검증됨
          {% elif vref.status == "metadata_error" %}🟠 메타데이터 오류
          {% elif vref.status == "hallucination" %}🔴 환각 의심
          {% elif vref.status == "unverifiable" %}❓ 확인 불가
          {% endif %}
        </span>
      </div>

      {# Bibliographic detail line #}
      <div class="ref-meta">
        {% if ref.journal %}<i>{{ ref.journal }}</i>{% endif %}
        {% if ref.volume %}, {{ ref.volume }}{% if ref.issue %}({{ ref.issue }}){% endif %}{% endif %}
        {% if ref.pages %}, pp. {{ ref.pages }}{% endif %}
        {% if ref.doi %} · DOI: {{ ref.doi }}{% endif %}
      </div>

      {# One-line verdict summary #}
      {% if vref.status == "hallucination" %}
        <div class="ref-summary" style="color:#c62828">❌ 4개 DB와 웹 검색에서 찾을 수 없음 — 가짜 인용 의심</div>
      {% elif vref.status == "unverifiable" %}
        <div class="ref-summary" style="color:#6a1b9a">❓ 확인 불가 — 수동 검증 권장</div>
      {% elif vref.status == "metadata_error" %}
        {% set crit_fields = [] %}
        {% set major_fields = [] %}
        {% set minor_fields = [] %}
        {% for f, sev in vref.diff_severities.items() %}
          {% if sev == "critical" %}{% set _ = crit_fields.append(f) %}
          {% elif sev == "major" %}{% set _ = major_fields.append(f) %}
          {% elif sev in ("minor","info") %}{% set _ = minor_fields.append(f) %}
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
        {% if vref.preprint_vs_published %}
          <div class="ref-summary" style="color:#1976d2">ℹ️ 1년 차이 (preprint vs 공식 출판) — 공식 출판 연도 권장</div>
        {% elif crit_fields %}
          <div class="ref-summary" style="color:#c62828">❌ 중요한 메타데이터 오류: {{ crit_fields|join(", ") }}</div>
        {% elif major_fields %}
          <div class="ref-summary" style="color:#ef6c00">⚠️ 메타데이터 차이: {{ major_fields|join(", ") }}</div>
        {% elif minor_fields %}
          <div class="ref-summary" style="color:#757575">ℹ️ 사소한 차이: {{ minor_fields|join(", ") }}</div>
        {% endif %}
      {% elif vref.status == "verified" %}
        {% if cfs %}
          <div class="ref-summary" style="color:#ef6c00">⚠️ 메타데이터는 정확하나 인용 내용에 문제가 있을 수 있습니다 ({{ cfs|length }}건)</div>
        {% else %}
          <div class="ref-summary" style="color:#2e7d32">✅ 메타데이터·인용 내용 모두 검증됨</div>
        {% endif %}
      {% endif %}

      {# Original raw text (truncated) #}
      {% if vref.reference.raw_text %}
        <div class="ref-raw">원문 그대로: {{ vref.reference.raw_text.strip()[:300] }}{% if vref.reference.raw_text|length > 300 %}…{% endif %}</div>
      {% endif %}

      {# Diff table — only when there are flagged differences. For
         unverifiable refs, the canonical may be a different paper that
         shares the first author; frame it as a candidate, not authoritative. #}
      {% if vref.field_diffs and vref.canonical %}
        {% if vref.status == "unverifiable" %}
          <div class="ref-meta" style="color:#ef6c00">
            ⚠️ 아래는 검색에서 가장 가까운 후보지만 실제 인용한 논문이 아닐 수 있습니다.
            같은 저자의 다른 논문일 가능성이 있어 직접 확인이 필요합니다.
          </div>
        {% endif %}
        <table class="diff-table">
          <tr>
            <th class="col-field">필드</th>
            <th class="col-user">사용자 인용</th>
            <th class="col-canon">실제 논문</th>
          </tr>
          {% for sev_name in ["critical", "major", "minor", "info"] %}
            {% for field_name, pair in vref.field_diffs.items() %}
              {% if vref.diff_severities.get(field_name, "minor") == sev_name %}
                {% set field_labels = {"title":"제목","authors":"저자","year":"연도","journal":"저널","doi":"DOI","volume":"권","issue":"호","pages":"페이지"} %}
                <tr>
                  <td class="col-field sev-{{ sev_name }}">● {{ field_labels.get(field_name, field_name) }}</td>
                  <td class="col-user">{{ pair[0] or "(없음)" }}</td>
                  <td class="col-canon">{{ pair[1] or "(없음)" }}</td>
                </tr>
              {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
          {% endfor %}
        </table>
      {% endif %}

      {# Hallucination explainer #}
      {% if vref.status == "hallucination" %}
        <div class="hall-explainer">
          이 참고문헌은 4개 학술 DB와 웹 검색에서 모두 찾을 수 없어 LLM이 생성한 가짜 인용일 가능성이 높습니다.
          직접 확인 후 삭제하거나 올바른 출처로 교체하세요.
        </div>
      {% endif %}

      {# Up to 2 content findings — side-by-side quote comparison.
         Skip for unverifiable refs (the content agent may have run against
         a different paper and its verdict is unreliable). #}
      {% for f in cfs %}{% if vref.status != "unverifiable" %}
        <div class="content-finding">
          <div class="cf-header">
            📝 {{ f.error_type or "내용 불일치" }}
            <span style="color:#c62828">{% for _ in range(f.severity) %}●{% endfor %}{% for _ in range(5 - f.severity) %}○{% endfor %}</span>
            <span style="color:#666; font-weight:normal; margin-left:0.6em">신뢰도 {{ f.confidence }}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="cf-pair">
            <div class="cf-side">
              <h5>초안 인용</h5>
              <div class="cf-quote cf-draft">
                {% if f.draft_claim_quote %}{{ f.draft_claim_quote }}{% else %}<em class="empty">(인용 문장 없음)</em>{% endif %}
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cf-side">
              <h5>원문 근거</h5>
              <div class="cf-quote cf-source">
                {% if f.source_evidence_quote %}{{ f.source_evidence_quote }}{% else %}<em class="empty">(원문에서 근거 인용 못 찾음)</em>{% endif %}
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          {% if f.explanation %}
            <div class="cf-explanation"><b>설명:</b> {{ f.explanation }}</div>
          {% endif %}
          {% if f.suggestion %}
            <div class="cf-suggestion">💡 <b>제안:</b> {{ f.suggestion }}</div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      {% endif %}{% endfor %}
      {% if vref.status != "unverifiable" and all_cf|length > cfs|length %}
        <div class="cf-extra">
          … 비슷한 발견 {{ all_cf|length - cfs|length }}건 추가 — 상위 {{ cfs|length }}건만 표시 (전체는 JSON에서 확인 가능).
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  {% endfor %}

  {# ---------- Orphan citations ---------- #}
  {% set orphan_findings = [] %}
  {% for f in report.findings %}
    {% if f.error_type in ("orphan_citation",) %}
      {% set _ = orphan_findings.append(f) %}
    {% endif %}
  {% endfor %}
  {% if orphan_findings %}
    <div class="orphan-section">
      <h2>본문 인용이 참고문헌과 매칭되지 않음</h2>
      {% for f in orphan_findings %}
        <div class="orphan-item">
          <b>{{ f.error_type }}</b> · {{ f.explanation }}
          {% if f.suggestion %}<div style="margin-top:0.3em">💡 {{ f.suggestion }}</div>{% endif %}
        </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  {% endif %}
</body>
</html>
